Repeat: sl 1, k2, (sl 1, k1) twice, sl 1, k2, (sl 1 , k4) twice
Purl all the purl stitches (these were knit stitches on the previous row); and slip, with yarn in front, all the slipped stitches from the previous row.
sl 1, k4, sl 1, k2, (sl 1, k1) twice, sl 1, k2, sl 1, k4
Purl all the purl stitches (these were knit stitches on the previous row); and slip, with yarn in front, all the slipped stitches from the previous row.
(sl 1, k4) twice, sl 1, k2, (sl 1, k1) twice, sl 1, k2
Purl all the purl stitches (these were knit stitches on the previous row); and slip, with yarn in front, all the slipped stitches from the previous row.
(k1, sl 1) twice, k2, sl 1, (k4, sl 1) twice, k2, sl 1
Purl all the purl stitches (these were knit stitches on the previous row); and slip, with yarn in front, all the slipped stitches from the previous row.
